<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1514948-just-read-an-interview-with-tan-twan-eng">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Just read an interview with Tan Twan Eng and was surprised to read this as I failed to pick up this aspect:<br />Interviewer: 'The story of Philip and his lover Endo-san is very much a story about forbidden love—in terms of sexuality, and because of the historical moment; the story is set during the Occupation and Endo-san is Japanese...<br />TTE: 'Yes, and there's the age difference as well.'<br />Any other reader pick this up? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
