<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">yes, early in the book when Phillip meets Endo it is stated that he is a man in his late forties. So this is a love affair between a 16 year old boy a<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">yes, early in the book when Phillip meets Endo it is stated that he is a man in his late forties. So this is a love affair between a 16 year old boy and a 48 year old man.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
