    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer24941248" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5644864710180396063">This is one of the best books I&apos;ve read in years. At it&apos;s core it&apos;s about doing the right thing in a very gray world -- a world where the right thing and the wrong thing are hardly distinguishable. It&apos;s about moving forward after you&apos;ve made a choice. <br/><br/>I wept for the staggering grief in Phillip Hutton&apos;s life, and I applauded the young man who set forth to do the right thing, no matter how murky that might be. <br/><br/>In addition to the great story, the author did a stellar job with invoking the setting a</span>
  <span id="freeText5644864710180396063" style="display:none">This is one of the best books I've read in years. At it's core it's about doing the right thing in a very gray world -- a world where the right thing and the wrong thing are hardly distinguishable. It's about moving forward after you've made a choice. <br /><br />I wept for the staggering grief in Phillip Hutton's life, and I applauded the young man who set forth to do the right thing, no matter how murky that might be. <br /><br />In addition to the great story, the author did a stellar job with invoking the setting and the history so essential to the story.<br /><br />I hope everyone will read this book. </span>
  <a data-text-id="5644864710180396063" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
